2002-1767 (La. 10/14/02)

Billye S. COHEN, et vir v. BROOKSHIRE BROTHERS INC., et al. No. 2002-C-1767. Supreme Court of Louisiana. Oct. 14, 2002.

In re Brookshire Brothers Inc. et al.; Super One Foods; — Defendants); Applying for Writ of Certiorari and/or Review, Parish of Rapides, 9th Judicial District Court Div. A, No. 196,335; to the Court of Appeal, Third Circuit, No. 01-1159.

Denied.

VICTORY, J., would grant the writ. TRAYLOR, J., would grant the writ.
